original_title: Kichatna: A Big Wall First Ascent In The Alaskan Range
overview: In Kichatna, Graham Zimmerman, accompanied by Dave Allfrey and Whit Magro, explores his motivation to ascend one of the most remote, big walls in the Alaska Range. Follow these American climbers into the stunning and steep landscape of the Kichatna Spires as they pursue a unique first ascent requiring versatile expertise in both big wall climbing and alpinism.
tagline: What do we seek from the experience of climbing?
title: Kichatna: A Big Wall First Ascent In The Alaskan Range
